    "Fashion parsing is one of the most fundamental problems in fashion computing, as numerous high-level fashion tasks such as virtual try-ons, fashion retrieval, etc.",
    "are performed based on the output of fashion parsing.",
    "The issue of how to improve the efficiency of fashion parsing while maintaining accuracy is therefore the goal of many researchers.",
    "In Page 17 of 41 67",
    "addition, expanding the categories of items that can be parsed is also an exciting topic in this field."
